    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>《降临之地》是一场诡谲循环的Roguelike卡牌策略之旅。在这款令人上瘾的构筑游戏中，你将打造独一无二的牌组、一键自动战斗、利用超过300种卡牌与遗物的疯狂连锁反应，挑战强大的使徒Boss！</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>它们带来光，那光是唯一的颜色。</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>它们带来歌，那歌是唯一的声调。</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>动态构建的牌组：在四大氏族构成的卡库中谨慎购买你的卡牌和遗物！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/864564caa35c72ef83b8ebd282e74248.poster.avif?t=1772101966\" width=1170 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/864564caa35c72ef83b8ebd282e74248.webm?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/864564caa35c72ef83b8ebd282e74248.mp4?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/4d875a2ce51a0aeb3564b500716aa7c7.poster.avif?t=1772101966\" width=1170 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/4d875a2ce51a0aeb3564b500716aa7c7.webm?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/4d875a2ce51a0aeb3564b500716aa7c7.mp4?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>连锁触发：通过不同的卡牌组合来发挥更强大的力量，打败使徒！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/1cf15ca8811aa921e5a131417a81ccca.poster.avif?t=1772101966\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/1cf15ca8811aa921e5a131417a81ccca.webm?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/1cf15ca8811aa921e5a131417a81ccca.mp4?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>启动仪式：变换、摧毁、添加烙印...参与各种影响深远的事件。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/28388c93ab71678a1cc360e4851c2598.poster.avif?t=1772101966\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/28388c93ab71678a1cc360e4851c2598.webm?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/28388c93ab71678a1cc360e4851c2598.mp4?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>镶嵌宝石：提升你的卡牌能力。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/d55425289c27e374efb78e850948e163.poster.avif?t=1772101966\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/d55425289c27e374efb78e850948e163.webm?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/d55425289c27e374efb78e850948e163.mp4?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>自动战斗：数回合内击败使徒，不死不休！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/b97a2f5b3c4ac9b89c0b7bd21c5b2176.poster.avif?t=1772101966\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/b97a2f5b3c4ac9b89c0b7bd21c5b2176.webm?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060830/extras/b97a2f5b3c4ac9b89c0b7bd21c5b2176.mp4?t=1772101966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
